<a href="/questions/555322-will-this-be-a-difficult-read-for-a">Will this be a difficult read for a British seventeen year old who has only recently gotten back into reading?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_555322'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F682804.The_Killer_Angels">like</a></span>

