<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/26175.To_the_Last_Man"><img alt="To the Last Man: A Novel of the First World War" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1425016018l/26175._SX98_.jpg" />
